	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="#regest1">
				<ab>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Gratia Christi tecum.</s>
				</ab>
				<ab>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Commendamus vobis bonum hunc et, quantum iudicare potuimus, solide pium Michaelem<note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1">Unbekannt.</note>, quem sesquimensem, ni fallor, in ptochodochio<note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2">Armenhaus (griech. <foreign xml:lang="el">πτωχοδοχεῖον</foreign> s. <persName ref="47">Dasypodius</persName>, Dic. 192r.</note> nostro fovimus diutius etiam foturi, si diutius hęrere voluisset.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ad laborandum<pb type="edition" next="442"/> manibus ob lęsum brachium inutilis est redditus; in spetiem superstitiosus videri poterit et nobis profecto primo occursu<note xml:id="fna" type="footnote" n="a">occursu <hi>nach einem gestrichenen, unlesbar gemachten Wort.</hi></note> talis videbatur; sed pressum<note xml:id="fnb" type="footnote" n="b"><hi>In der Vorlage</hi> pressus.</note> intuentes et illius animam, quatenus licuit, discutientes, longe alium invenimus.</s>
				</ab>
				<ab>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Reiicula veste<note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote" n="3">mit einem verbrauchten (s. <persName ref="47">Dasypodius</persName>, Dic. 96v.) Gewand.</note> et nudis pedibus ingreditur absque caligis, quod vereatur, ne, si decentiore toga et caligis utatur, impotenti [m]ilitandi<note xml:id="fnc" type="footnote" n="c">[m]ilitandi <hi>am Rand nachgetragen und im engen Einband teilweise verdeckt.</hi></note> affectu vincatur; id quod prius etiam accidisse sibi valde conquęritur.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Supra modum enim militiam, cuius ab adulescentia assuetus fuit, ardet, ut consilium hoc improbare haudquaquam valeamus.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Puto vere in Christum collocatum, quicquid huic benignitatis exhibetur<note xml:id="fn4" type="footnote" n="4">Vgl. Mt 25, 40.</note>.</s>
				</ab>
				<ab>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Bene vale, mi charissime frater.</s>
				</ab>
				<ab>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="565">Constantiae</placeName>, 7. octobris anno 1544.</s>
				</ab>
				<ab>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus Ambr. Bl.</s>
				</ab>
				<ab>
					<note type="address">[Adresse auf der Rückseite:]</note>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Suo longe colendissimo fratri d. Heinricho Bullingero.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tiguri.</s>
				</ab>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
